title: Spacious Top Floor End Unit, Dual Pane, Carport
posting_body: ['Spacious Top Floor End Unit, Dual Pane, Carport, Close to Valley Medical Center!', 'Property Address', '2135 Marlboro Court - 6 | San Jose, CA 95128', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Presidential Real Estate, Inc', 'Description', '2135 Marlboro Court #6, San Jose, CA 95128 (Fruitvale/Del Mar)', 'Spacious and charming upstairs 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment located in West San Jose.', 'The apartment has a spacious living room, large windows, and lots of closet space.', 'Good size kitchen with lots of cabinets and counter space.', 'The apartment includes fresh paint, dual pane windows, and 1 car carport.', 'Water and garbage are included.', 'One year lease required.', 'No pets except for required service animals.', 'The apartment is centrally located close to Valley Medical Center, restaurants, shopping with convenient access to highway 280 and 17.', 'Cal DRE# 01998337', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,825.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,500.00']
